Introduction

Kim Do Hee, formerly known as High.D, is a South Korean singer under KH Company. She is a former member of the girl group SONAMOO. She was a contestant on Girls On Fire and V-1 (Vocal No.1).

She made her solo debut on April 23, 2022 with the digital single "Goodbye Answer".
